"<emphasis>on</emphasis>. Check this option only if you know what you are "
"doing. &mdn;s are considered a nuisance (or are simply ignored) by a lot of "
"people. It is better to request them only when necessary."
msgstr ""
"Hvis dette er markeret vil <xref linkend=\"composer-options-request-mdn\"/> "
"som standard være <emphasis>til</emphasis>. Markér kun dette hvis du ved "
"hvad du foretager dig. &mdn;'er opfattes som en irritation (eller ignoreres "
"simpelthen) af en masse mennesker. Det er bedre at beslutte sig for at "
"spørge dem et brev af gangen."

